column5: here are a few pics of the many we got on the weekend. Hope you enjoy and many more to come i might be heading out torrmow moarning if anyone wants to come please feel free to pm me or call me at 905 436 0202 i will be up late dont be afraid to call. thanks bigredfisher        and i had to add these
Nice fish!!!  Although, I'd be removing your phone number with the quickness if I were you   If someone wants it, they'll PM you.
Nice fish! Is that a jig in the chinnies mouth or a strip leech? Regardless, that's pretty cool.
Great report and pics bigredfisher  It looks a little nippy on the pics..... Great job Thanks for sharing Leechman
WOOHOOH.  BIG MAN.    Nice feesh.  HD
Definitely not the Big Manistee, it's much larger  .

Ahh the mighty Manistee..  One day!!  Our local waters are such trickles.  Frog water really..  But I love them all the same.  The challenges small creeks present keep me keen and sharp.  Ya outta come try one of my tribs for a change..  In fact, I challenge you.  HD
Nice fish Bigredfisher! When Im less busy with school, I'll definitely join you on these Steelhead outings!
